{"tid":2120644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食衛局聘用華昇 屬同系 華大基因兩公司 同列黑名單","createTime":"2020-07-22T21:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T02:22:47.000Z","uid":53379,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6b817be1eec8973932496f091d220f0b103ae725","tid":2120644,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T21:55:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">華大基因兩公司 同列黑名單</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】被美國商務部列入實體黑名單的11間企業當中，有兩間被指控涉嫌強制採集維族人基因研究，以進一步打壓維族人。兩企分別是新疆絲路華大基因科技與北京六合華大基因科技，與早前香港食物及衛生局以「有迫切需要於最短時間內開展大規模檢測以保障公眾健康」為由，直接聘用為香港提供病毒檢測的華昇診斷中心，均同屬內地生物科技企業深圳華大基因。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/daily2.php?node=1595358111723&amp;issue=20200722&amp;fbclid=IwAR0sgKKBKpAqQA0X0gSJY1iZttHGTeRsHrsXjtrkfNWBZotrn6opRMadiEI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Fdaily2.php%3Fnode%3D1595358111723%26issue%3D20200722%26fbclid%3DIwAR0sgKKBKpAqQA0X0gSJY1iZttHGTeRsHrsXjtrkfNWBZotrn6opRMadiEI&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgKQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=f902a42e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Fdaily2.php%3Fnode%3D1595358111723%26issue%3D20200722%26fbclid%3DIwAR0sgKKBKpAqQA0X0gSJY1iZttHGTeRsHrsXjtrkfNWBZotrn6opRMadiEI&h=f1b1966c\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/daily2.php?node=1595358111723&amp;issue=20200722&amp;fbclid=IwAR0sgKKBKpAqQA0X0gSJY1iZttHGTeRsHrsXjtrkfNWBZotrn6opRMadiEI</a>"},{"pid":"036cfe91237cc8540292f3adb4e86456e2e1ce9e","tid":2120644,"uid":269578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T21:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3abdb91a4e2e39d2698a8c179a424cfe89c207","tid":2120644,"uid":267410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T22:07:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a466aaac6460f3e6b6cf2f5dda0d7ca4f7059cba","tid":2120644,"uid":6